---

## 🚀 Overview  

**ft_transcendence** is the final project of the **42 Network curriculum**, where you build a **full-stack real-time web application**.  
It’s a modern reinvention of the **classic Pong** game — featuring multiplayer gameplay, chat, authentication, monitoring, and deployment.

> 🧠 This project brings together everything from backend APIs, real-time systems, and authentication to frontend frameworks, containerization, and observability.

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack  

| Layer | Technologies |
|:------|:--------------|
| **Frontend** | React.js • TailwindCSS • TypeScript |
| **Backend** | Fastify.js • Socket.IO • JWT • OAuth2 |
| **Database** | SQLite |
| **Deployment** | Docker • Nginx • HTTPS |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus • Grafana |

---

## ✨ Features  

### 🧩 Backend (Fastify + Socket.IO)
- ⚡ Fast, scalable backend using **Fastify**
- 🔌 Real-time gameplay powered by **Socket.IO**
- 🔒 Authentication with **JWT** and **2FA**
- 🌐 **OAuth2** for remote login (Google)
- 🧱 Modular, production-ready architecture (Docker + Nginx)

---

### 👥 User Management & Authentication
- 🧍 User registration and profile management  
- 🔑 Login via **JWT** and **OAuth2**  
- 🔐 Enable **Two-Factor Authentication (2FA)**  
- 🏆 Manage users across tournaments  
- 📜 View match history, wins/losses, and statistics  

---

### 🕹️ Gameplay & Matchmaking
- 🎮 Real-time Pong gameplay with **Socket.IO**
- 🌍 Play remotely against other players
- ⚙️ Customizable gameplay (speed, color, mode…)  
- 🔄 Handles lag and reconnections gracefully  
- 🧠 Includes a **second bonus game**

---

### 💬 Live Chat
- 💭 Real-time chat between players  
- 🔔 Notifications for friend requests, matches, and messages  
- 🚫 Block unwanted users  
- 🕹️ Send game invitations directly from chat  

---

### 🗄️ Database (SQLite)
- 🪶 Lightweight and portable database  
- 💾 Stores users, chats, matches, and configurations  

---

### 🎨 Frontend (React + TailwindCSS + TypeScript)
- ⚛️ Built with **React.js** and **TypeScript**  
- 📱 Responsive across **desktop, tablet, and mobile**  
- ⚡ Real-time UI updates with **Socket.IO**  
- 🧭 Clean, modular, and maintainable architecture  

---

### 📊 Monitoring & Deployment
- 🧠 **Prometheus** collects metrics from **Node Exporter** (system metrics: CPU, RAM, disk usage) and **Nginx Exporter** (web server performance)  
- 📈 **Grafana** visualizes real-time dashboards for system and network performance  
- 🚨 **Alerting**: Prometheus triggers alerts based on Node and Nginx metrics (e.g., high CPU usage, low memory, server down)  
- 🐳 **Dockerized** for easy deployment  
- 🌐 **Nginx** ensures HTTPS and reverse proxy routing  

---

### 🌍 Cross-Platform Support
- 💻 Works on all modern browsers  
- 📱 Fully responsive and mobile-friendly  
- 🈳 Multilingual support (EN / FR / ES)

---

## 🏁 Conclusion  

**ft_transcendence** is a full-stack, real-time web app that combines gaming, authentication, and observability into one modern platform.  
It’s designed to demonstrate complete mastery of web technologies — from frontend to backend, infrastructure to UX.

💡 Built with passion, code, and a bit of Pong magic. 🏓
